              name: 'Enable Apps from Unknown Sources',
              text: 'On your Firestick go to Settings → My Fire TV → Developer Options and turn on "Apps from Unknown Sources" and "ADB Debugging".',
              url: 'https://iptv-usa-omega.vercel.app/install-iptv-smarters-pro-firestick#step1',
            },
            {
              '@type': 'HowToStep',
              position: 2,
              name: 'Install the Downloader App',
              text: 'Press the Home button, go to the Search icon and type "Downloader". Install the free Downloader app by AFTVnews from the Amazon App Store.',
