              },
            },
            {
              '@type': 'Question',
              name: 'Why is IPTV Smarters Pro buffering on my Firestick?',
              acceptedAnswer: {
                '@type': 'Answer',
                text: 'Buffering is usually caused by a slow internet connection or an overloaded IPTV server. IPTV Smarters PRO uses 50+ global servers with anti-freeze technology to eliminate buffering. Make sure your Firestick is connected to a 2.4GHz or 5GHz Wi-Fi network with at least 25 Mbps for 4K streams.',
