    tagline="FIRESTICK SETUP GUIDE"
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1593359677879-a4bb92f829d1?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80',
      alt: 'Amazon Firestick with IPTV Smarters Pro installed showing live TV channels',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      How to Install <span class="text-accent dark:text-white">IPTV Smarters Pro</span><br />
      on Firestick — 2025 Guide
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      Get <strong>IPTV Smarters Pro</strong> running on your Amazon Firestick in under 10 minutes. This step-by-step guide
      covers everything — from enabling sideloading to entering your
      <strong>IPTV Smarters PRO</strong> subscription credentials and streaming 20,000+ channels in 4K.
    </Fragment>
