  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
       STEPS — The core install guide
  ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <Steps
    title="How to Install IPTV Smarters Pro on Firestick"
    subtitle="Follow these 6 steps exactly — no technical knowledge required. The entire process takes less than 10 minutes."
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Step 1: Enable Apps from Unknown Sources',
        description:
          'On your Firestick remote press the <strong>Home</strong> button → go to <strong>Settings</strong> (top menu) → select <strong>My Fire TV</strong> → tap <strong>Developer Options</strong>. Enable both <strong>"Apps from Unknown Sources"</strong> and <strong>"ADB Debugging"</strong>. This allows you to sideload the IPTV Smarters Pro APK. Note: this is a standard Amazon feature — no jailbreak involved.',
        icon: 'tabler:settings',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 2: Install the Downloader App',
        description:
          'Press the <strong>Home</strong> button and click the <strong>Search (magnifying glass)</strong> icon. Type <strong>"Downloader"</strong> in the search box. Select the <strong>Downloader</strong> app by AFTVnews and click <strong>Download</strong>. This free app is available directly on the Amazon App Store and is the safest way to sideload IPTV Smarters Pro on Firestick.',
        icon: 'tabler:download',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 3: Download the IPTV Smarters Pro APK',
        description:
          'Open the <strong>Downloader</strong> app. In the URL / Search bar, type the IPTV Smarters Pro APK download URL (we recommend using the official link from the IPTV Smarters Pro website: <strong>iptvsmarters.com</strong>). Tap <strong>Go</strong> and wait for the download to complete — usually under 60 seconds on a normal connection.',
        icon: 'tabler:file-download',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 4: Install the IPTV Smarters Pro APK',
        description:
          'Once the APK has downloaded, a prompt will appear automatically. Tap <strong>Install</strong> and wait for the installation to finish (30–60 seconds). When done, tap <strong>Done</strong> — do NOT tap Open yet. Return to Downloader and delete the APK file to free up storage space on your Firestick.',
        icon: 'tabler:package',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 5: Launch IPTV Smarters Pro & Add Your Playlist',
        description:
          'Find <strong>IPTV Smarters Pro</strong> in your Apps list (or search for it). Open the app and tap <strong>"Login with Xtream Codes API"</strong>. Enter your <strong>IPTV Smarters PRO</strong> credentials: the <strong>Server URL</strong>, <strong>Username</strong>, and <strong>Password</strong> sent to your email after purchase. Alternatively, select <strong>"Load Your Playlist or File/URL"</strong> and paste your M3U URL. Tap <strong>Add User</strong>.',
        icon: 'tabler:login',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 6: Start Streaming in 4K',
        description:
          'Your full IPTV Smarters PRO library will load automatically — <strong>20,000+ live TV channels</strong>, <strong>100,000+ VOD movies and series</strong>, full <strong>EPG TV Guide</strong>, catch-up TV, and premium sports. Browse by category, search for channels, or go directly to live sports. Enjoy buffer-free 4K streaming on your Firestick.',
        icon: 'tabler:player-play',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461151304267-38535e780c79?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80',
      alt: 'Firestick remote and TV showing IPTV channels after installing IPTV Smarters Pro',
    }}
  />

