    title="IPTV Smarters Pro on Firestick — Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Everything you need to know about installing and using IPTV Smarters Pro on Amazon Firestick."
    columns={1}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Can I install IPTV Smarters Pro directly from the Amazon App Store?',
        description:
          'IPTV Smarters Pro is not listed on the Amazon App Store, so it cannot be installed directly. You must sideload it using the Downloader app — which IS free on the App Store. The process takes under 10 minutes and requires no technical experience. Follow the steps above exactly.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Is it safe to sideload IPTV Smarters Pro on my Firestick?',
        description:
          'Yes. Sideloading is a built-in Amazon feature designed specifically to allow apps not in their store. Enabling "Apps from Unknown Sources" does NOT void your warranty or harm your device. Always download the APK from the official IPTV Smarters Pro website to ensure you get the genuine, safe version of the app.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do I need to jailbreak my Firestick?',
