  <CallToAction
    title="Ready to Stream on Your Firestick?"
    subtitle="Get your IPTV Smarters PRO subscription today and be watching 20,000+ live channels in 4K on your Firestick within 10 minutes. Instant activation. 7-day money-back guarantee."
